{"tid":2375636,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大女生路軌放竹枝囚8個月上訴刑期 李運騰：已屬寬大 原打算加刑","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T10:25:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"120f3929b0f2b0742118d4db5f2a3745b7fe969b","tid":2375636,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:29:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13159&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Tf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=6b1a6a7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13159</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第廿八庭<br />\n#李運騰法官 #1111大埔<br />\n👤盧(21) #宣讀判詞 <br />\n<br />\n控罪: <br />\n⑥ 抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n⑦ 危害他人安全 #鐵路罪行 <br />\n被控於2019年11月11日在大埔公路元洲仔近燈柱EC0659天橋將一些竹枝非法及惡意放在或擲於大埔墟鐵路上，或放或擲而致橫於該鐵路上。<br />\n<br />\n控罪⑥判處2個月即時監禁<br />\n控罪⑦判處8個月即時監禁<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8591&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Tf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=bee15f08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8591</a> <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n刑期上訴詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12571&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Tf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=ee3b0c04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12571</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🛑結果：<br />\n刑期上訴被駁回。<br />\n刑期維持原判，即時監禁8個月。<br />\n高等法院判案書 (<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=133140&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D133140%26currpage%3DT&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Tf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=329a601f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=133140&amp;currpage=T</a>)"},{"pid":"4e834eb5a1eec05b6110b3a8e3951646b5f3b332","tid":2375636,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e650b5ae39e565c4efc84dfbfde7d769833cf5dc","tid":2375636,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"21歲中大女生前年11月11日「大三罷」，在大埔火車軌上投擲竹枝及拒捕，被判囚8個月。她不服刑罰過重向高院提上訴，今遭高等法院法官李運騰駁回。李官在判辭中形容，刑期已經是相當寬大，甚至可以說是略低，若非她的良好背景和年輕等個人情況，上訴庭還打算上調刑期。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人透過律師反映，原審裁判官由起初便沒有考慮社會服務令，而且沒有適當地考慮感化主任正面建議。<br />\n<br />\n但法官認為，被告的罪行不但威脅鐵路系統穩定運作和車上司機和乘客安全，而且萬一列車出軌，可能會牽連毗鄰民居，故判刑同須要一定阻嚇力，防止他人有樣學樣。上訴人求情稱受社會事主犯案，但法官不接納為求情理由，因為她選擇用非法和不和平的手段，漠視別人權利，強迫別人被動參與他們的「大三罷」，是為自私，目無法紀及文明社會不能接受的，上訴人請求法庭考慮社會服務令，是不切實際的。<br />\n<br />\n但法官不同意原審裁判官以上訴人沒有勸阻未成年人退出示威，作為她的加刑理由。因為沒有證據反映她知悉對方是成年或否。"},{"pid":"2ae49836f33f3c72e1c9fae1c98e67288d503a79","tid":2375636,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"點解會去咗高等法院"},{"pid":"c7bc171c79dce44738e8ad16404dedbfedaef5ba","tid":2375636,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cd18ba8082f8a5bf445fddd1c6145cec1756b6","tid":2375636,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗跪埋係到講謝主隆恩呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73965a9fcffbf058082ea299bdcf43160f2d90fc","tid":2375636,"uid":156321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ae49836f33f3c72e1c9fae1c98e67288d503a79","tid":2375636,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"點解會去咗高等法院"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:33:20.000Z","msg":"上訴咪去高院囉"},{"pid":"df19fd2685ddef0ec311e1fca97450c3ed9d0e98","tid":2375636,"uid":277888,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"<code>強迫別人被動參與他們的「大三罷」</code><br />\n<br />\n強迫別人被動參與他們的逃犯條例<br />\n強迫別人被動參與他們的禁蒙面法<br />\n強迫別人被動參與他們的國安法<br />\n強迫別人被動參與他們的限聚令"},{"pid":"6ec19b4688ae451d78bf602716ca2fddc76bbf66","tid":2375636,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ae49836f33f3c72e1c9fae1c98e67288d503a79","tid":2375636,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"點解會去咗高等法院"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"裁判法院案被告上訴刑期會交俾高等法院原訟庭單一法官審"},{"pid":"ce6294fb9c513b5646a6a77a9d2831621fb4ca13","tid":2375636,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e956c5b443d411b0280a27a5132a51f63794cf","tid":2375636,"uid":64337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"李運騰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756f030adb77ebb422fbecf520d56652c7290dcb","tid":2375636,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae49836f33f3c72e1c9fae1c98e67288d503a79","tid":2375636,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"點解會去咗高等法院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"罪名刑期上限14年，一般法院點審？"},{"pid":"5751ab4934cf908608ac9ac7401bdf25cbd003b6","tid":2375636,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"重新判刑 <br />\n<br />\n36. 基於以上， 本席有須要重新判刑。本席考慮到本案的所有背景和事實，亦考慮到上訴人的個人情況 &mdash; 包括她認罪，以及「背景報告及感化主任報告」的內容等求情理由。基於上訴人的良好背景，以及她仍相對年輕，本席認為適合給她較寬大的處理：參見律政司司長訴SHY 。然而，因着控罪的嚴重性及判刑須具阻嚇力，本席維持兩項控罪的判刑。這對上訴人來說，已經是相當寬大，甚至可以說是略低。若非因為她的個人情況，本席原本打算將該罪的判刑上調。<br />\n<br />\n37. 就整體刑期方面，本席維持8個月監禁的總刑期，因此下令兩項控罪的刑期同期執行。"},{"pid":"c5e7cb63b7e22cb59086193f0789ddf11a3846ab","tid":2375636,"uid":326287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:39:43.000Z","msg":"咁大班大學生比人拉晒坐監，中年之後 會點樣對返社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ec16a12938c933695f648e2857518e643e3ca9","tid":2375636,"uid":33498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"所以當年皇軍殺得幾萬南京人已屬寬大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3b3a0aa04b16e939388c879cacd703cecf4a1a","tid":2375636,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"756f030adb77ebb422fbecf520d56652c7290dcb","tid":2375636,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae49836f33f3c72e1c9fae1c98e67288d503a79","tid":2375636,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"點解會去咗高等法院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"罪名刑期上限14年，一般法院點審？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"暴動最多坐十年<br />\n咪一樣去晒只可以判七年嘅區院審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係睇律政司覺得會判幾多先去邊個院啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be5341f1bd1bce0248a9b375e12628d1a30331c","tid":2375636,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"